ass=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>use</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xlink:</span>href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#segment<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">transform</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rotate(36)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>use</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xlink:</span>href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#segment<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">transform</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rotate(54)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>use</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xlink:</span>href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#segment<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">transform</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"t